hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1801fe98d9d1f06ba9d422b1aa0763e0e2e143a2","tid":497344,"uid":10442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:51:33.000Z","msg":"尹志田指港燈有信守承諾，將２０１４至２０１８年的５年間電費凍結在２０１３年的水平<br />\n。港燈先在頭兩年凍費，後兩年減費，雖然明年抉因燃料費特別回扣減少而令電費回升，但整體<br />\n５年來說，２０１８年電費仍較２０１３年低１６﹒６％。<br />\n<br />\n嘩 你講撚晒啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e80e415aeaa4081ed652c8351a88149d801bff","tid":497344,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:59:27.000Z","msg":"段紅字真係好中國特色<br />\n寫小說咁寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ed7ba8a76fddba46ecb6eca43c88b67f7ce244","tid":497344,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>勁<br />\n林鄭真係有料過習總多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支持佢取代習總成為國家主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我要林鄭，習包子下台</blockquote><br />\n習包子下台<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 林鄭</blockquote><br />\n林鄭有咁上下民意支持既時候，可以擁立佢做總統</blockquote><br />\n淋奠香港大總統！！！！！"},{"pid":"4e71507afa83fc2f31907f0ea213473e67adb4d4","tid":497344,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>勁<br />\n林鄭真係有料過習總多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支持佢取代習總成為國家主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做大個聲勢俾北京知</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal